text: Inđić, also transcribed as Indjić, is a Serbian surname. Notable people with the surname include: *Aleksandar Inđić (born 1995), Serbian chess grandmaster *Đorđe Inđić (born 1975), Bosnian Serb football manager and former footballer *Eugen Indjic (born 1947), Serbian-born American pianist Category:Serbian- language surnames
title: Inđić
